    <briefdescription>
<para>Constant symbols are unchangeable named memory addresses. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Symbols may be named function or global objects that have been exported for linking. These constant symbols are useful in the base image as they may be placed in ROM.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>When updating this structure, make sure to also update the &apos;scripts/build/llext_prepare_exptab.py&apos; build script. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
